name: The Vase Occasional Table - Davidson
description: The Vase Occasional Table forms part of the vibrant Wanderlust Collection and is a fun but graceful example of contemporary British furniture design. This chic design is ideal for those who want to inject a burst of colour and is available in a wide range of different shades to create different moods in high gloss and satin. These tables also look incredibly smart in any of Davidson's signature timber finishes.
